### Elasticsearch 索引创建（REST Client / VS Code REST Client 插件）
### 变量
@host = http://localhost:9200

### 1. 求职事实（与 Chroma 向量侧 fact_id 对齐）
PUT {{host}}/job_advisor_facts
Content-Type: application/json

< ./job_advisor_facts.json

### 2. 职位全文检索（可选，与 MongoDB jobs 同步写入）
PUT {{host}}/job_advisor_jobs
Content-Type: application/json

< ./job_advisor_jobs.json
